n terms of the computational cost, the proposed SVM-ROMs\nand SVR-ROMs are $\\mathcal{O}(10^7)$ times faster than running a high-fidelity\nnumerical simulation for evaluating QoIs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Aug 2019 20:12:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-15"}
