uations 261 (2016), 505-537] in the critical\ncase, while extending and improving some results from [Chen-Zou, Arch. Ration.\nMech. Anal. 205 (2012), 515--551], [Guo-Luo-Zou, Nonlinearity 31 (2018),\n314--339].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2019 08:20:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2019 16:01:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-02"}
