stics, we feed it into our framework. Results show\nthat, even with few data points, extrapolating a continuous model makes it\npossible to estimate the global optimum configuration almost instantaneously.\nThe very same tool can then be used to achieve any further optimization goal on\nthe same input parameters in negligible time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2019 13:43:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 12:30:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-29"}
